<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='458000' id='t-458000'>I want to say a few words about vision.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='460000' id='t-460000'>When I started this program four years ago,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='463000' id='t-463000'>I had this original plan</span>
