<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='473000' id='t-473000'>in my mind.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='475000' id='t-475000'>And it took me exactly two months</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='478000' id='t-478000'>of complete frustration</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='480000' id='t-480000'>to realize that this vision</span>
