<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='528000' id='t-528000'>Together with the kids,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='530000' id='t-530000'>I also went through a remarkable transformation.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='533000' id='t-533000'>Now, I come from a cutthroat world</span>
