<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='590000' id='t-590000'>And one of these principles</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='592000' id='t-592000'>is focus.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='594000' id='t-594000'>Before each ride</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='596000' id='t-596000'>we sit together with the kids,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='598000' id='t-598000'>and we give them one word</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='600000' id='t-600000'>to think about during the ride.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='602000' id='t-602000'>You have to focus their attention on something</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='605000' id='t-605000'>because so many things happen.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='607000' id='t-607000'>So these are words like &quot;teamwork&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='609000' id='t-609000'>or &quot;endurance&quot;</span>
