<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='617000' id='t-617000'>You know, perspective</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='619000' id='t-619000'>is one of these critically important</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='621000' id='t-621000'>life-coping strategies</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='623000' id='t-623000'>that mountain biking can really teach you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='626000' id='t-626000'>I tell kids</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='628000' id='t-628000'>when they struggle through some uphill</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='631000' id='t-631000'>and feel like they cannot take it anymore,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='633000' id='t-633000'>it really helps to ignore the immediate obstacles</span>
