<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='655000' id='t-655000'>Now, let me give you an example of how it works.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='657000' id='t-657000'>You stand with your bike at the beginning of February.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='660000' id='t-660000'>It's very cold, and you're standing in one of these rainy days,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='663000' id='t-663000'>and it's drizzling</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='665000' id='t-665000'>and cold and chilly,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='668000' id='t-668000'>and you're standing in, let's say, Yokneam.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='671000' id='t-671000'>And you look up at the sky through a hole in the clouds</span>
