<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='708000' id='t-708000'>And so we talked about</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='710000' id='t-710000'>these special words that we teach them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='712000' id='t-712000'>And at the end of each ride, we sit together</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='715000' id='t-715000'>and share moments</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='717000' id='t-717000'>in which those special words of the day</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='720000' id='t-720000'>popped up and made a difference,</span>
