<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='739000' id='t-739000'>and went away together with my brother.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='742000' id='t-742000'>We walked 120 kilometers</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='744000' id='t-744000'>until we reached Sudan.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='746000' id='t-746000'>This was the first place where we got some water and supplies.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='749000' id='t-749000'>And he goes on saying, and everyone looks at him like a hero,</span>
