<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='762000' id='t-762000'>and he says, &quot;And this was just the beginning</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='764000' id='t-764000'>of our ordeal</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='766000' id='t-766000'>until we ended up in Israel.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='768000' id='t-768000'>And only now,&quot; he says,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='770000' id='t-770000'>&quot;I'm beginning to understand where I am,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='772000' id='t-772000'>and I actually like it.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='774000' id='t-774000'>Now I remember, when he said it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='776000' id='t-776000'>I felt goosebumps on my body,</span>
